"title": "2024: Jesus Christ, glory of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2024",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ's radiance and splendour reflects the glory of the Father, and is both revealed to and reflected in the lives of believers.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's glory existed before the incarnation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:5\">JHN 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's glory is God's glory</h2>\n<h3>God's glory is reflected in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:41\">JHN 12:41</a> <em>John makes no distinction between God's glory revealed in <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">Isa 6:3</a> and the glory of Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:32\">JHN 13:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ brings glory to his Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13\">JHN 14:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:31\">JHN 13:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1\">JHN 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:27\">ROM 16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:12\">EPH 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:25\">JUD 1:25</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit glorifies Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:14\">JHN 16:14</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's glory is revealed on earth</h2>\n<h3>Through his miracles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:11\">JHN 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:4\">JHN 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:40\">JHN 11:40</a></p>\n<h3>To his disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:28-Luke9:32\">LUK 9:28–9:32</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:1-Matt17:2\">MAT 17:1–17:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:2-Mark9:3\">MRK 9:2–9:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3\">ACT 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:6\">ACT 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:13\">ACT 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>In his death and resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23\">JHN 12:23</a></strong> <em>One of the major themes of John's Gospel is that Jesus Christ is glorified through his death and resurrection.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:39\">JHN 7:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:16\">JHN 12:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:13-Acts3:15\">ACT 3:13–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:21\">1PE 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9\">HEB 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>The glory of the exalted Christ</h2>\n<h3>His appearance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:13-Rev1:16\">REV 1:13–1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55-Acts7:56\">ACT 7:55–7:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:18\">REV 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11-Rev19:16\">REV 19:11–19:16</a></p>\n<h3>He receives glory from all creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:13\">REV 5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:21\">HEB 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:6\">REV 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:11-Rev5:12\">REV 5:11–5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:12\">REV 7:9–7:12</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's glory will be revealed at the second coming</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:38\">MRK 8:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:26\">LUK 9:26</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:27\">MAT 24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">MAT 24:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">MRK 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">LUK 21:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">MAT 25:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:7\">2TH 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">2TH 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:13\">TIT 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's glory is shared by believers</h2>\n<h3>As they become like him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:22\">JHN 17:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>At the end of time</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17-Rom8:18\">ROM 8:17–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">COL 3:4</a></p>",
